#

Honey-Mustard Glazed Roast Pork

$25
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Mustard

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

PorkRoastedComfort FoodDinner

Description

Tender roast pork with a sweet and tangy honey-mustard glaze, served with roasted vegetables and creamy mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Pork Loin: 2 lbs
  • Honey: 1/2 cup
  • Dijon Mustard: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Carrots: 2 cups, chopped
  • Zucchini: 2 cups, chopped
  • Potatoes: 3 cups, peeled and diced
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Milk: 1/2 cup
